mber of shortcomings:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>They favor historical popularity over <a href=\"\/keyword-relevancy\" title=\" keyword popularity\">relevance<\/a>. Just because a keyword has a high search volume doesn\u2019t mean it\u2019s relevant to your business.<\/li>\n<li>The results aren&#8217;t actionable: They just dump out a list with no organization or tips on how to use the terms.<\/li>\n<li>The results aren&#8217;t exclusive, so you have no competitive edge.<\/li>\n<li>Results are just a sampling of the vast array of real search terms that are typed into Google every day. You&#8217;ll miss out on hundreds of long-tail variations that could apply to your search campaigns.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><a href=\"\/keywords\">Our own Free Keyword Tool<\/a> is a vast improvement over other available keyword phrase generators. Because we aggregate over a billion unique keywords and constantly update our database, our keyword suggestions are far more relevant and accurate.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/new-free-keyword-tool-cars-industry-results-21-1024x578.png\" alt=\"new-free-keyword-tool-cars-industry-results\" width=\"1024\" height=\"578\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-48510 size-large\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/new-free-keyword-tool-cars-industry-results-21-980x553.png 980w, https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/new-free-keyword-tool-cars-industry-results-21-480x271.png 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) and (max-width: 980px) 980px, (min-width: 981px) 1024px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<p>However, even with this much longer, more relevant keyword list, you still need a way to incorporate exclusive long-tail keyword data. How?<\/p>\n<h2><strong>Finding Keyword Phrases the WordStream Way<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>The <a href=\"\/free-keyword-tools\">WordStream Keyword Research Suite<\/a> includes a keyword phrase generator that overcomes all these weaknesses. The Keyword Research Suite includes tools for:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Finding hundreds or thousands of keyword phrases relevant to your business<\/li>\n<li>Finding targeted clusters of related keywords to use in search marketing campaigns<\/li>\n<li>Organizing a list of keywords into small groups by relevance<\/li>\n<li>Finding negative keywords to reduce wasteful PPC spending<\/li>\n<li>Optimizing your content so it gets found in the search engines<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Best of all, our keyword tools are completely free.<\/p>\n<h2><strong>Use WordStream to Identify Longer, Niche Keyword Phrases<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>Yet another way WordStream&#8217;s keyword tools beat out the competition is by allowing you to capitalize on the <a href=\"\/long-tail\" title=\" long tail seo\">long tail of search<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>Studies show that search engine users are getting more advanced and using longer, more detailed keyword phrases. This is great for search marketers, since long keyword phrases show more <a href=\"\/keyword-intent\" title=\"keyword intent\">intent<\/a> and often indicate that the user is late in the buying cycle.<\/p>\n<p>But your typical free keyword tool isn&#8217;t going to show you all those hundreds of long-tail, <a href=\"\/niche-keywords\" title=\" Finding Keywords in Your Industry or Niche\">niche keyword phrases<\/a>. You&#8217;ll mostly get a short list of very high-volume, one- or two-word keywords that are totally obvious, with tons of <a href=\"\/articles\/ultimate-guide-to-keyword-competition\">keyword competition<\/a> in the SERPs. By looking at the long tail, you&#8217;ll have a much better chance of ranking high in search results, and your AdWords ads and landing pages will be more specific and relevant to the search queries. Increased relevance is good for organic SEO, improves your Quality Score, kickstarts conversions, lowers your ad spend and adds more value to your entire account.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"\/free-keyword-tools\">Try our free keyword tools now!<\/a><\/p>\n<p><input type=\"hidden\" id=\"hippowiz-ass-injected\" value=\"true\" \/><input type=\"hidden\" id=\"hvmessage-toextension-listener\" value=\"none\" \/><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Keyword phrase research is the first step in conducting search engine optimization and pay-per-click marketing campaigns. You need to be able to \u201cspeak the searcher\u2019s language\u201d to help them find what they&#8217;re looking for \u2013 and what you&#8217;re offering. But too often, search marketers make the mistake of looking at keyword phrase discovery as a [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":223,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"_et_pb_use_builder":"","_et_pb_old_content":"","_et_gb_content_width":"","om_disable_all_campaigns":false},"class_list":["post-48168","learn","type-learn","status-publish","hentry"],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v25.8 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Keyword Phrases: Finding the Best Keyword Phrases for Your Business<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Finding the most relevant keyword phrases for your site can be difficult. Try our Keyword Phrase Generator to find your most profitable keywords.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/keyword-phrases\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Keyword Phrases: Finding the Best Keyword Phrases for Your Business\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Finding the most relevant keyword phrases for your site can be difficult. Try our Keyword Phrase Generator to find your most profitable keywords.\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" 